5, 145.7593, 145.2565, 143.4682, 143.237, 143.9101, 143.824, 144.4556, 142.8065, 144.9218, 146.0936, 147.0062, 147.1202, 147.3962, 147.243, 147.2345, 147.8587, 149.0767, 149.193, 148.8232, 148.6188, 148.1317, 149.53, 150.4743, 150.5033, 151.3059, 150.5995, 151.5613, 152.1979, 151.9139, 151.3427, 150.267, 149.7743, 150.1096, 150.2879, 151.2975, 150.788, 150.8008, 150.9395, 151.0639, 150.9463, 150.0957, 150.4752, 149.2142, 148.5547, 148.12, 147.08, 145.3184, 145.5336, 146.381, 146.2335, 146.429, 145.3705, 144.9683, 144.828, 143.3597, 142.2443, 144.1834, 144.2582, 142.2594, 143.6925, 142.8319, 141.9717, 144.912, 144.0323, 143.0265, 142.4699, 144.8521, 142.9857, 142.9954, 142.0687, 142.4149, 141.5903, 143.5652, 143.797, 143.7987, 143.5199, 145.0708, 145.1798, 145.6577, 146.0283, 144.3182, 145.0661, 146.376, 143.154, 143.327, 143.8023, 144.1448, 142.1886, 141.9986, 141.2378, 140.8138, 139.6103, 136.5868, 137.3217, 137.1184, 135.9697, 137.0227, 138.9574, 139.3126, 137.9693, 140.2976, 141.4293, 142.0576, 140.4658, 140.1263, 139.1159, 138.6538, 138.2062, 138.5742, 140.8075, 137.6906, 137.5114, 135.9677, 141.9674, 138.0644, 140.8811, 139.0936, 140.5864, 140.6024, 140.3497, 144.5117, 142.3396, 141.6207, 139.9834, 139.9803, 139.6358, 138.0488, 137.3644, 137.1245, 137.8879, 138.3466, 141.2449], "summary_html": "<h1>量价齐飞 FLY 因子 | 通过 (Sharpe 1.21)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>该因子捕捉\"量价齐飞\"现象——当价格与成交量（换手率）呈现高度正相关时，暗示短期过度投机行为，预示未来价格回落。核心逻辑基于行为金融学：散户处置效应和庄家投机周期导致\"放量上涨\"的股票在下一期表现不佳。因子值越高（量价同向越强），做空信号越强。</p>\n<p>将此逻辑迁移到商品期货市场：用收盘价与换手率（volume/opi）的滚动相关系数作为因子，截面排名后反向做多空组合。高 FLY 品种（过度投机）做空，低 FLY 品种做多。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.76</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>2.9%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-10.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.96</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.45</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.03 / 0.91</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.63</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.62</span></td><td>0.36</td><td>1.94</td><td>0.9</td><td>0.74</td><td>1.07</td><td>0.94</td><td>1.58</td><td>1.7</td><td>1.33</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.61</span></td><td>0.91</td><td>1.64</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.61</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 40 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 40 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.7</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>核心因子（原文定义）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">FLY_t^i = \\text{corr}(P_\\tau^i, \\text{Turn}_\\tau^i), \\quad \\tau \\in [t-W+1, t]</div>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">P_\\tau^i</span>：品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在时刻 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\tau</span> 的收盘价</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{Turn}_\\tau^i = \\text{Volume}_\\tau^i / \\text{OPI}_\\tau^i</span>：换手率代理变量（成交量 / 持仓量）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">W</span>：回望窗口（最优 60 日）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>仓位构建：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_t^i = (0.5 - \\text{rank}_t^{cs}(FLY_t^i)) \\times 2</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_t^i = \\text{vol\\_target\\_scale}(\\text{rebalance\\_hold}(\\text{signal}, H), \\sigma_{target}=0.15)</div>\n<p>变形因子：</p>\n<ul><li>FLY_R2: <span class=\"math-tex\">FLY_{R2} = \\rho^2</span>（忽略方向，只看拟合度）</li>\n<li>FLY_cut: 截尾处理，去除低价 40% 数据后再算相关性</li>\n<li>FLY_vol: 直接用 volume 替代 turnover</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.54, turnover 0.91, vol_target_scale 在 rebalance 之前导致换手过高</td><td>修复操作顺序: rebalance_hold 先于 vol_target_scale; 扩展 hold 到 [20,40]; 添加 turnover/volume 两种 proxy</td><td>Sharpe 0.54 -&gt; 1.21, 多个变体 &gt;0.8</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>所有 gate 通过, Sharpe 1.21; window=60 + hold=40 + cs 归一化最优; R2 (corr^2) 表现差; IC gate 变体被去重</td><td>聚焦 window [40,60], 加 hold=60; 添加 vol_target [0.10, 0.20] 变体; 移除表现差的 R2 和短窗口</td><td>Sharpe 微升至 1.2146; hold=60 反而变差 (0.51); vol_target 变化影响不大</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>收敛: Sharpe 1.21 稳定, 年度 Sharpe 均&gt;0 (除 2023 -0.01); 半程 Sharpe: 前半 1.11, 后半 1.51</td><td>确认最优参数; decision=skip</td><td>最终 Sharpe 1.21, 策略稳定</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R1 -&gt; R2 的 Sharpe 翻倍（0.54 -&gt; 1.21）源于两个改动：(1) 修正 rebalance/vol_target 顺序避免每日换仓，(2) 将 hold_days 从 20 增至 40 大幅降低换手成本。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（59 个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 约 40 个交易日（月度偏长）</li>\n<li><strong>因子类型</strong>: 截面反转/过度投机类</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 原文为 A 股选股因子，跨资产到商品期货有效但 IC 偏低（0.015 截面, 0.007 时序）\n<p>- 2023 年 Sharpe 接近零，该年策略几乎无收益 - 截面标准化（_cs）对提升 Sharpe 作用很大，说明因子量纲在品种间差异较大 - 换手率代理变量（volume/opi）非精确换手率，在 opi 数据缺失品种退化为纯 volume</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9959</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.24s</li>\n</ul>"}